com.cgoab.offline.ui.thumbnailviewer
Class ThumbnailHolder

java.lang.Object
  com.cgoab.offline.ui.thumbnailviewer.ThumbnailHolder

public class ThumbnailHolder
extends java.lang.Object

Holder for thumbnail image data and associated detail such as filename and cached meta-data. The ImageData may be loaded on a background thread, thus at any given time the image may be null, #hasImage() can be used to test for this case.
